Principal Component Analysis of Cross-covariance between phenotype and genvironment. <PG>
* genvironment = genotype + (micro-)environment.

-p=0 => P = p(e0)
-p=1 => P = p(e1)
-p=2 => P = p(e1) - p(e0)

-eg=0 -> G = G(e0) (+)* e0
-eg=1 -> G = G(e1) (+) e1
-eg=2 -> G = [G(e1) (+) e1] - [G(e0) (+) e0]

(+) indicates direct sum.